{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/AboutTitle.png?t=1649774786\" /><br>Hell Loop is a platformer tower defense game, unlike any other tower defense game you know. You are not defending anything valuable. You are torturing sinners who are continually marching, one by one in a long streak, trying to evade their punishment. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/_g1.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/MechanicsTitle.png?t=1649774786\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Select.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Select from a random subset of available traps - get each game a different choice!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Place.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Place traps carefully across the level - you can do it in pause mode or in real-time<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Upgrade.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Watch the bloodshed and upgrade traps<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Manage.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Manage your resources of blood - upgrades and placing traps cost blood, kills earns blood<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Mod.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Take into account the passive modifiers for the game - they can be both positive and negative!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/FeaturesTitle.png?t=1649774786\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Tower defense meets platformer - a unique combo with a pinch of good old Lemmings vibe (only the Lemmings were cute, our humans are not).<br></li><li> Hand-crafted levels with unique challenges. After all who says that hell is only fire and lava. A sinner can very well be tortured in acid or put to work in mines!<br></li><li> Select wisely when given the option, as new traps will not come every level.<br></li><li> Be aware of game-changing modifiers.<br></li><li> Calculate with your blood, every drop of it is important. Killing human grants you a few extra drops.<br></li><li> Don't forget to upgrade your traps! No one said being the hell manager is easy.&quot;\t<br></li><li> Steam achievements &amp; leaderboard!\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Three Levels!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473870/3fa42e3ee2b078c81ac04b7c79e43dc72f491222.jpg"},{"name":"50 Humans Killed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473870/f5e7847dc5ccc35c1cde8d3a68026b1a284e6e1f.jpg"},{"name":"500 Humans Killed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473870/76a458ba75bcaa63f7ff6079ac36c85014771163.jpg"},{"name":"5000 Humans Killed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473870/df2aacec76acf04e04deede858876727b56d0cf0.jpg"},{"name":"Catch Them All","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473870/1b182f21f388deedfda4e4366d821388ac040ebc.jpg"},{"name":"Second Spawn Gate Unlocked","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473870/ff4178855d1e9a281ce6305109a581bb0b058094.jpg"},{"name":"Pacific Approach","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1473870/72aa391fa996e05e4d10b48a9bc71901f8b74230.jpg"},{"n