 streak, trying to evade their punishment. <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/_g1.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/MechanicsTitle.png?t=1649774786\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Select.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Select from a random subset of available traps - get each game a different choice!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Place.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Place traps carefully across the level - you can do it in pause mode or in real-time<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Upgrade.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Watch the bloodshed and upgrade traps<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Manage.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Manage your resources of blood - upgrades and placing traps cost blood, kills earns blood<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/HellLoop-Mod.gif?t=1649774786\" /><br>Take into account the passive modifiers for the game - they can be both positive and negative!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1473870/extras/FeaturesTitle.png?t=1649774786\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Tower defense meets platformer - a unique combo with a pinch of good old Lemmings vibe (only the Lemmings were cute, our humans are not).<br></li><li> Hand-crafted levels with unique challenges. After all who says that hell is only fire and lava. A sinner can very well be tortured in aci